            Phone: <a href="tel:+491732118910" class="hover:text-brand-accent transition-colors">+49 173 2118910</a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-heading text-brand-light mb-3">VAT</h2>
          <p>
            No VAT identification number under § 27a UStG has been issued.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-heading text-brand-light mb-3">Responsible for content under § 18 (2) MStV</h2>
          <p>
            Adem Kocyigit<br />
            Tiefe Allee 33<br />
            24149 Kiel<br />
            Germany
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-heading text-brand-light mb-3">Dispute resolution</h2>
          <p>
            I am neither willing nor obliged to participate in dispute resolution proceedings before a consumer arbitration board.
          </p>
