        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-heading text-brand-light mb-3">Liability for content</h2>
          <p>
            As a service provider, I am responsible for my own content on these pages under § 7 (1) DDG and general laws. However, under §§ 8 to 10 DDG, as a service provider I am not obliged to monitor transmitted or stored third-party information or to investigate circumstances that suggest unlawful activity.
